              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A counter telescope consisting of",
                "a silicon p-n junction diode preceded by a gas",
                "proportional counter with offset center wire. Signals",
                "from the gas proportional counter, proportional to",
                "dE/dX and from the silicon counter, proportional to",
                "the energy E, a fed in to the two sides of a pulse",
                "multiplier  network.   The output from this network",
                "identifies the detected particle as protons, deuterons",
                "or alpha particle, etc."
              ]
            }
